A few days ago, @stefanolsdal got together with Sally A. Edwards + Sarah J. Edwards, who featured on the cover of the 'Without You I'm Nothing' album, to talk about how the now infamous cover came together and how they came to star on the artwork. 
Visit the http://wyin.placeboworld.co.uk website and look in the exclusive section for the interview. 
#wyin20

In celebration of the 20th Anniversary of 'Without You I'm Nothing' we've launched a new site which will collate your memories of the album. 
Tag a memory post on instagram with #WYIN20 to be included on the website, you will also be automatically entered into a prize draw to win a copy of the album on vinyl, or a 'Without You I'm Nothing' Picture Disc!  LINK IN BIO
